  <section id="creditor-claims" class="sec">
    <h2>7. The Creditor Claims</h2>
    <p class="sec-lead">
      Citgo&rsquo;s parent company shares are the target of approximately
      $21&nbsp;billion in competing creditor claims, making this one of the most
      complex multinational asset disputes in recent history.
    </p>

