          <p>
            Citgo operates three refineries in the United States: (1)&nbsp;Lake Charles,
            Louisiana, with 432,000&nbsp;bpd capacity&mdash;the company&rsquo;s largest
            facility; (2)&nbsp;Lemont, Illinois, with 172,000&nbsp;bpd capacity, serving
            the Chicago and Midwest markets; and (3)&nbsp;Corpus Christi, Texas, with
            165,000&nbsp;bpd capacity on the Gulf Coast. Combined, these three refineries
